        "text": "paregeneto (sing.)",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " would imply that the Virgin took a specially prominent part in the incident. Joseph is never mentioned after the scene in the Temple. This incident can hardly be the same as those in ",
